from the accident,

00:18:39.000 --> 00:18:40.360
and should heal after a few days of rest.

00:18:40.360 --> 00:18:41.680
But her left wrist

00:18:42.000 --> 00:18:43.480
and lumbar spine are badly injured.

00:18:43.480 --> 00:18:44.360
Has she had

00:18:44.360 --> 00:18:46.040
