00:18:57.880 --> 00:18:58.320
Haimeng.

00:18:58.320 --> 00:18:59.120
I'm fine.

00:18:59.880 --> 00:19:01.520
I don't need another surgery.

00:19:01.520 --> 00:19:02.200
Ms. Ye,

00:19:02.640 --> 00:19:03.200
